子当时所在地点离车库至少有8-10米，如果驾驶员正常行驶是能看到小孩的。 不仅如此，他还表示，驾驶员存在超速和逆行问题，第三方机构出具的鉴定书上，小轿车的车速是13-14千米每小时，而地下车库和小区限速牌上写的都是限速5千米每小时。 记者联系到驾驶员龙某的丈夫高先生，他在电话中表示，出口入口都是出入口，地下车库并没有线，但记者反驳到地下车库的出口入口写的很清楚。 记者询问高先生，妻子当时有没有看到小孩？ 高先生称是走到跟前来不及刹车了，地库斜坡出来往前，刚好那个时间段又是对着太阳，“等我老婆出事之后，她连小孩玩滑板车都不知道”。 高先生表示，妻子现在情绪不太好，后续所有事情他来处理，“该给小孩补偿补偿，接下来都听交警，一步一步安排，没有异议我老婆就给关进去了”，还称希望能和孩子父母见面谈一谈。"},"attached_info":"CkEI6rr0qdWc3vZLEAMaCTExMTQ5NzM5MSD/qoi5BjAAOLoDQA5yCjI2MDM4MDA1NzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"4.6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-72a59c5fb1480be10f95a5d30fc5c0b6_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1730565042.308069","card_id":"Q_2837384109","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":2837384109,"title":"如何看待马龙奥林匹克独家专访中暂无退役计划且还未考虑未来当教练这一举动?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/2837384109","type":"question","created":1730475807,"answer_count":22,"follower_count":25,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[24972,1330455],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"[5 张图片]"},"attached_info":"CkAI6rr0qdWc3vZLEAMaCTExMTU0NDA1OSCf7pO5BjAAOBlAD3IKMjgzNzM4NDEwOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"3.9 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-a41036b8466031e1b80dd76a07083d57_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1730565042.308709","card_id":"Q_2793388886","target":{"id":2793388886,"title":"如何评价卡普生命卡惊现霸王色？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/2793388886","type":"question","created":1730443621,"answer_count":27,"follower_count":38,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_tok